    "body": "It depends on the beacon node. If the BN has a fee recipient set then it will be used, but the VC doesn't have a way of knowing that so I think a 404 response is most feasible.\r\n\r\nIn the case where the BN doesn't have a fee recipient, the funds are burnt at the 0x01 address: https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/aa022f46855df2a1420a6a80a788c73dc2779aa7/beacon_node/execution_layer/src/lib.rs#L57-L65",
